<% content_for :hero_unit do %>
<div class="hero-unit">
  <%= image_tag 'store/maggie.png', :style => 'float: left; margin-right: 20px'%>
  <h1>Your Picture. Quilted Art.</h1>
    
    <p class='lead' style="margin: 10px 0 0" >We turn your favorite photograph into a stunning art quilt.</p>
    <p style="margin: 0px"><%= link_to "Order One Today", "/products/custom-portrait-quilt", :class => 'btn btn-success btn-xlarge' %></p>
    <div class="fb-like" data-href="http://www.portraitsinfabric.com" data-send="false" data-layout="button_count" data-width="450" data-show-faces="false" data-font="arial"></div>
</div>
<% end %>
<div id="process" class="row">
  <h1>What we do.</h1>
  <%= image_tag 'store/portrait_process.png' %>
  <ul class="steps">
  <li>
    <strong>1</strong>
    <h4>Your Photograph</h4>
    <p>Having a clear and in focus photograph is key to getting the best reproduction. The subject will be the focus of the wall hanging.</p>
  </li><li>
    <strong>2</strong>
    <h4>Design & Layout</h4>
    <p>After the image is chosen for the wall hanging, We then begin to design the layout and choose the colors that best enhance the piece.</p>
    </li>
    <li>
    <strong>3</strong>
    <h4>Pieced & Quilted</h4>
    <p>Each individual piece is painstakingly cut out from fabric and sewn on the background. The backing, binding and hanging method are then attached. </p>
  </li><li>
    <strong>4</strong>
    <h4>A Priceless Keepsake</h4>
    <p>Your picture quilt will be something you cherish for years to come. We can honestly say that our picture quilts have brought some of our clients to tears.</p>
  </li>
</ul>
</div>
<hr class="soften">
<div id="gallery" class="row">
	<h3>Recently commissioned portraits.</h3>
	<ul class="thumbnails">
	<% Spree::Gallery.recent.each do |gallery| -%>
  <li class="span3">
    <a href="#" >
      <%= image_tag(gallery.pictures.first.attachment.url(:product), :class => 'img-polaroid') %>
    </a>
  </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

</div>
